Description: adversarial safety harness for the MCPwn execution engine
 mcpwn-red validates whether Parrot OS MCPwn deployments can be subverted by
 malicious YAML tool definitions, prompt-injection output, container boundary
 weaknesses, or unconstrained cross-tool chaining.
 .
 The runtime dependency on python3-mcp may require separate source packaging if
 the MCP SDK has not yet landed in the target Parrot or Debian archive.
